snippet.title: Ultreïa - Trailer #1
snippet.description:
Add to wishlist on STEAM :
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1284870/Ultrea/

Ultreïa is a Point'n Click adventure game.
A little robot Nymo, fueled by a great loss, becomes a pilgrim and decides to cross a wild world to find the meaning of life and death. He also has a mysterious goal : to find a guy called Cheyenne. 

Find more here: 
➥ Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/greewook/ 
➥ Twitter - https://twitter.com/greewook 
➥ Facebook https://www.facebook.com/greewook 

A Graphic Adventure by Olivier De Rop
Music by Yann Latour
